### Genfeed API - Opus Pro Integration Endpoints
### Manage Opus Pro template-based video generation
### Handles: video generation, templates, account info

########################################
# Service Status
########################################

### Check Connection Status
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/opuspro/status
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Templates
########################################

### Get Available Templates
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/opuspro/templates
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Video Generation
########################################

### Generate Video from Template
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/opuspro/generate
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "templateId": "{{opusProTemplateId}}",
  "params": {
    "title": "My Video Title",
    "text": "Content for the video"
  }
}


### Check Video Generation Status
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/opuspro/status/{{opusProVideoId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


########################################
# Webhook (Public)
########################################

### Simulate Webhook Callback (completed)
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/v1/webhooks/opuspro/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "callback_id": "{{metadataId}}",
  "status": "completed",
  "videoUrl": "https://cdn.opus.pro/example-video.mp4"
}


### Simulate Webhook Callback (failed)
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/v1/webhooks/opuspro/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "callback_id": "{{metadataId}}",
  "status": "failed",
  "error": "Template rendering failed"
}


########################################
# Test Cases
########################################

### Test: Invalid Video ID
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/opuspro/status/invalid-id
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Unauthorized Access
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/integrations/opuspro/generate
